title: Crocodile Dundee II. (Captioned)
creator_credit: John Cornell, Jane Scott and Paramount Pictures
brief_description: Begins in New York where Dundee now lives with his journalist girlfriend. In order to escape the pursuit of an international drug ring who have murdered her former husband, Dundee and his girlfriend return to the Australian outback where Dundee is well prepared to confront them.
